# Project Context

This is a python project using fastapi.
It is a monorepo with workspaces: genie-agent-sdk (packages\genie-agent-sdk), rag_service (services\rag_service), registry (services\registry).

The API has 25 routes. See .codesight/routes.md for the full route map with methods, paths, and tags.
Middleware includes: custom, auth.

High-impact files (most imported, changes here affect many other files):
- /api.py (imported by 1 files)
- /ingestion.py (imported by 1 files)
- /retrieval.py (imported by 1 files)
- /completion_gate.py (imported by 1 files)
- /executor.py (imported by 1 files)
- /orchestrator.py (imported by 1 files)
- /planner.py (imported by 1 files)
- /router.py (imported by 1 files)

Required environment variables (no defaults):
- AGENT_ADVERTISE_HOST (packages\genie-agent-sdk\.env.example)
- AGENT_ADVERTISE_PORT (packages\genie-agent-sdk\.env.example)
- AGENT_INVOKE_TOKEN (packages\genie-agent-sdk\.env.example)
- GENIE_API_KEY (.env.example)
- GENIE_CONFIG_FILE (src\genie\platform\config.py)
- LOG_LEVEL (services\registry\src\registry_service\service.py)
- MCP_AUTH_TOKEN (packages\genie-agent-sdk\.env.example)
- MILVUS_TOKEN (src\genie\memory\adapters\vector.py)
- MILVUS_URI (src\genie\memory\adapters\vector.py)
- OPENAI_API_KEY (services\agents\.env.example)
- OPENAI_BASE_URL (packages\genie-agent-sdk\.env.example)
- OUTAGE_DATA_PATH (services\agents\mcp_weather_server.py)
- REGISTRY_AUTH_TOKEN (services\registry\.env.example)

